acle/oe_vertretungen_de.pdf |title=Archived copy |access-date=2017-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160110114113/http://www.bmeia.gv.at/fileadmin/user_upload/oracle/oe_vertretungen_de.pdf |archive-date=2016-01-10 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*{{Flag|Brazil}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://islamabade.itamaraty.gov.br/en-us/general_information.xml |title=General Information |website=Embassy of Brazil in Islamabad |accessdate=5 July 2019}}</ref>\n*{{Flag|Mexico}}<ref name=\"sre.gob.mx\"/>\n*{{Flag|Portugal}}<ref name=\"portugal.gov.pt\"/>\n*{{Flag|Slovakia}}\n*{{TUR}}<ref name=\"mfa.gov.tr\"/>\n\n== Accredited missions ==\nResident in [[Ankara]], [[Turkey]]:\n\n{| \n|\n*{{Flag|Albania}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mfa.gov.al/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=7208:where-to-aply-for-a-visa-to-enter-the-republic-of-albania&catid=129:where-to-aply-for-a-visa-to-enter-albania-&Itemid=66&lang=sq |title=Archived copy |access-date=2010-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220084231/http://www.mfa.gov.al/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=7208:where-to-aply-for-a-visa-to-enter-the-republic-of-albania&catid=129:where-to-aply-for-a-visa-to-enter-albania-&Itemid=66&lang=sq |archive-date=2016-12-20 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*{{Flag|Colombia}}\n*{{Flag|Estonia}}\n*{{Flag|Latvia}}\n*{{Flag|Lithuania}}\n*{{Flag|Macedonia}}<ref>[http://www.mfa.gov.mk/default1.aspx?ItemID=364{{dead link|date=August 2018}}]</ref>\n*{{Flag|Moldova}} \n*{{Flag|Mongolia}}\n|}\n\nResident in [[Tehran]], [[Iran]]:\n\n{| \n|\n*{{Flag|Croatia}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mvpei.hr/MVP.asp?pcpid=1615&dmid=147 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2010-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101115224139/http://www.mvpei.hr/MVP.asp?pcpid=1615#pocdrz |archive-date=2010-11-15 |url-status=dead }}</ref> \n*{{Flag|Gabon}} \n*{{Flag|Georgia}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mfa.gov.ge/index.php?sec_id=421&lang_id=ENG |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2008-03-01 |u