achi|work=Ministry of Foreign Affairs (Bahrain)|date=9 March 2017|accessdate=13 March 2017}}</ref>\n*{{CHN}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://karachi.china-consulate.org/eng/|title=Consulate General of the People's Republic of China in Karachi|website=karachi.china-consulate.org}}</ref>\n*{{FRA}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ambafrance-pk.org/Services-consulaires,17#karachi-1|title=Services consulaires|website=La France au Pakistan - Ambassade de France au Pakistan}}</ref>\n*{{DEU}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pakistan.diplo.de/Vertretung/pakistan/en/03Consulate/__The__Consulate__General.html |title=Archived copy |access-date=2016-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109080546/http://www.pakistan.diplo.de/Vertretung/pakistan/en/03Consulate/__The__Consulate__General.html |archive-date=2017-01-09 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*{{IDN}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kemlu.go.id/karachi/Pages/default.aspx?l=id |title=KJRI Karachi - Home |publisher=Kemlu.go.id |date=2010-04-26 |accessdate=2018-08-26}}</ref>\n*{{IRN}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://karachi.mfa.ir/index.aspx?siteid=243&pageid=7826 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2016-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227125754/http://karachi.mfa.ir/index.aspx?siteid=243&pageid=7826 |archive-date=2016-12-27 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*{{ITA}} <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conskarachi.esteri.it/consolato_karachi/en/|title=Consolato - Karachi|website=www.conskarachi.esteri.it}}</ref>\n*{{JPN}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kr.pk.emb-japan.go.jp|title=Consulate General of Japan in Karachi|website=www.kr.pk.emb-japan.go.jp}}</ref>\n*{{Flag|Kuwait}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mofa.gov.kw/En/Pages/default.aspx |title=Archived copy |access-date=2016-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227071531/http://www.mofa.gov.kw/En/Pages/default.aspx |archive-date=2016-12-27 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n*{{MYS}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kln.gov.my/web/pak_karachi/home |title=Portal - Home |publi