]]''\n| Jimmy\n|\n|-\n| 1935\n| ''[[Born to Gamble]]''\n| College Man at Senior Prom\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 1935\n| ''[[Man on the Flying Trapeze]]''\n| Claude Neselrode \n| Alternative title: ''The Memory Expert''\n|-\n| 1935\n| ''[[Alice Adams (1935 film)|Alice Adams]]''\n| Frank Dowling\n|\n|-\n| 1935\n| ''[[Dr. Socrates]]''\n| Grocery Store Clerk\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[The Singing Kid]]''\n| Young Man\n| (scenes deleted)\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[Palm Springs (1936 film)|Palm Springs]]''\n| Bud\n|\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[The Crime of Dr. Forbes]]''\n| Student Doctor\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[My Man Godfrey]]''\n| Charlie Van Rumple \n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[King of the Royal Mounted (film)|King of the Royal Mounted]]''\n| RCMP Const. Slim Callum\n|\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[Valiant Is the Word for Carrie]]''\n| Mat Burdon\n|\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[Pigskin Parade]]''\n| Mortimer Higgins\n|\n|-\n| 1936\n| ''[[Two Minutes to Play]]''\n| Hank Durkee\n|\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[She's Dangerous]]''\n| Drunk\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[Waikiki Wedding]]''\n| Everett Todhunter\n|\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[We Have Our Moments]]''\n| Clem Porter\n|\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[Turn Off the Moon]]''\n| Truelove Spencer\n|\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[Dangerous Holiday]]''\n| Max\n|\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[Behind the Mike (film)|Behind the Mike]]''\n| Curly Conway\n|\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[Stage Door]]''\n| Butch \n|\n|-\n| 1937\n| ''[[Love Takes Flight]]''\n| Donald\n|\n|-\n| 1938\n| ''[[Joy of Living]]''\n| Florist\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 1938\n| ''[[Vivacious Lady]]''\n| Culpepper\n|\n|-\n| 1938\n| ''[[Having Wonderful Time]]''\n| Gus\n| Alternative title: ''Having a Wonderful Time''\n|-\n| 1938\n| ''[[Three Loves Has Nancy]]''\n| George Wilkins, Jr.\n|\n|-\n| 1938\n| ''[[The Mad Miss Manton]]''\n| D.A.'s Secretary\n|-\n| 1938\n| ''[[A Man to Remember]]''\n| Raymond\n| Uncredited\n|-\n| 1938\n| ''[[Hard to Get (1938 film)|Hard to Get]]''\n| Stanley Potter\n|\n|-\n| 1939\n| ''[[You Can't Cheat an Honest Man]]''